quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  44,19,aur khuda ke samnay sar kashi nah karo. mein tumahray paas khuli Daleel le kar aaya hon
  44,20,aur is ( baat ) se ke tum mujhe sangsar karo apne aur tumahray perwar-digaar ki panah mangta hon
  44,21,aur agar tum mujh par imaan nahi laatay to mujh se allag ho jao
  44,22,tab moose ne apne perwar-digaar se dua ki ke yeh nafarman log hain
  44,23,( khuda ne farmaya ke ) mere bundon ko raton raat le kar chalay jao aur ( fravni ) zaroor tumhara taqub karen ge
  44,24,aur darya se ( ke ) khushk ( ho raha hoga ) paar ho jao ( tumahray baad ) un ka tamam lashkar duubo diya jaye ga
  44,25,woh log bohat se baagh aur chashmay chore gay
  44,26,aur khityan aur nafees makaan
  44,27,aur aaraam ki cheeze jin mein aishkiya karte they
  44,28,isi terhan ( howa ) aur hum ne dosray logon ko un cheezon ka maalik bana diya
  44,29,phir un par nah to aasman ko aur zameen ko rona aaya aur nah un ko mohlat hi di gayi
  44,30,aur hum ne bani Israel ko zillat ke azaab se nijaat di
  44,31,( yani ) firaon se. be shak woh sarkash ( aur ) hadd se nikla howa tha
  44,32,aur hum ne bani Israel ko ahal aalam se danista munhtakhibkiya tha
  44,33,aur un ko aisi nishanain di theen jin mein Sarih azmaish thi
  44,34,yeh log yeh kehte hain
  44,35,ke hamein sirf pehli dafaa ( yani aik baar ) marna hai aur ( phir ) uthna nahi
  44,36,pas agar tum sachey ho to hamaray baap dada ko ( zindah kar ) lao
  44,37,bhala yeh achay hain ya tba ki qoum aur woh log jo tum se pehlay ho chukay hain. hum ne un ( sab ) ko halaak kardiya. be shak woh gunehgaar they
  44,38,aur hum ne asmano aur zameen ko aur jo kuch un mein hai un ko khailtay hue nahi banaya
  44,39,un ko hum ne tadbeer se pedakiya hai lekin aksar log nahi jantay
